                FastSpring B.V. Strawinskylaan 3101 Tenant B.V. 1077 ZX Amsterdam, Netherlands<br />
                All rights reserved. <u>Privacy Policy</u> | <u>Terms of Use</u></p>
            </div>	
        </footer>
        <br/>
    </apex:define>
    
</apex:page>